    "body": "OK, I figured out why you're getting so many ambiguous event messages!  It's because you're using a proxy contract.  Sorry, Truffle has some trouble with these at the moment.  We're hoping to address these problems eventually; see issues #3826 and #3941.  It may be a while before we get to those, sorry.  But, at least the decodings are correct, even if there's no real ambiguity? :)\r\n\r\nAnyway, that still leaves the other problems, but at least I figured out what's up with the events.  I don't think you need to file a new issue for the event problems; we can track it in #3826 and #3941.  Thanks again for bringing this up!",
